# Ship pre-built Sunspot circuit artefacts so the issuer-service Dockerfile
# can bake them into the image without needing nargo/sunspot at build time.
# Artefacts live under backend/artefacts/ (regen step copies them there from
# circuits/target/). The *.pk rule above would otherwise hide the proving
# key, so we whitelist the three runtime files explicitly.
!backend/artefacts/zksettle_slice.json
!backend/artefacts/zksettle_slice.ccs
!backend/artefacts/zksettle_slice.pk
